        "status" : "generated",
        "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" data-fhir=\"generated\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"/><p style=\"border: black 1px dotted; background-color: #EEEEEE; padding: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px\">Expansion performed internally based on <a href=\"CodeSystem-attachment-tag.html\">codesystem Attachment Tag CodeSystem v1.0.0 (CodeSystem)</a><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag|1.0.0\" title=\"Click to Copy URL\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></p><p>This value set contains 3 concepts</p><table class=\"codes\" data-fhir=\"generated\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display (en)</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b>JSON</b></td><td><b>XML</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"x-http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag-inline-data-externalized-to-file\"> </a><code>http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"CodeSystem-attachment-tag.html#attachment-tag-inline-data-externalized-to-file\">inline-data-externalized-to-file</a></td><td>Inline data externalized to and saved as file</td><td><div><p>Indicates that the Attachment content was originally available\nas inline data/blob content but has been externalized and saved\nas a file in object storage, with the Attachment.url carrying\nthe storage location.</p>\n<p>If this tag is absent, the content SHALL be assumed to have\noriginated as an external file rather than inline data.</p>\n</div></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"{&quot;system&quot;: &quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;, &quot;version&quot;: &quot;1.0.0&quot;, &quot;code&quot;: &quot;inline-data-externalized-to-file&quot;, &quot;display&quot;: &quot;Inline data externalized to and saved as file&quot;}\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"&lt;coding&gt;&lt;system value=&quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;version value=&quot;1.0.0&quot;&gt;&lt;code value=&quot;inline-data-externalized-to-file&quot;&gt;&lt;display value=&quot;Inline data externalized to and saved as file&quot;&gt;&lt;/coding&gt;\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"x-http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag-duplicate\"> </a><code>http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"CodeSystem-attachment-tag.html#attachment-tag-duplicate\">duplicate</a></td><td>Duplicate of another attachment on the same element</td><td><div><p>Indicates that this attachment was created as a duplicate of the\ncontent in another attachment on the same element for some reason,\nfor example because the same content needed to be stored as two\ndifferent content types.</p>\n</div></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"{&quot;system&quot;: &quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;, &quot;version&quot;: &quot;1.0.0&quot;, &quot;code&quot;: &quot;duplicate&quot;, &quot;display&quot;: &quot;Duplicate of another attachment on the same element&quot;}\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"&lt;coding&gt;&lt;system value=&quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;version value=&quot;1.0.0&quot;&gt;&lt;code value=&quot;duplicate&quot;&gt;&lt;display value=&quot;Duplicate of another attachment on the same element&quot;&gt;&lt;/coding&gt;\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"x-http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag-hidden\"> </a><code>http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">\u00a0\u00a0<a href=\"CodeSystem-attachment-tag.html#attachment-tag-hidden\">hidden</a></td><td>Hidden from application use</td><td><div><p>Indicates to the consumer application that this attachment should\nnot be used even though it exists in the data.</p>\n<p>This may be used to identify the preferred/usable attachment when\nmultiple copies of equivalent content are available.</p>\n</div></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"{&quot;system&quot;: &quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;, &quot;version&quot;: &quot;1.0.0&quot;, &quot;code&quot;: &quot;hidden&quot;, &quot;display&quot;: &quot;Hidden from application use&quot;}\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td><td><span class=\"copy-text-inline\"><button data-clipboard-text=\"&lt;coding&gt;&lt;system value=&quot;http://314e.com/fhir/CodeSystem/attachment-tag&quot;&gt;&lt;version value=&quot;1.0.0&quot;&gt;&lt;code value=&quot;hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;display value=&quot;Hidden from application use&quot;&gt;&lt;/coding&gt;\" title=\"Click to Copy as Coding\" class=\"btn-copy\"> </button></span></td></tr></table></div>"
